## How Long Does SEO Take for Bradford Businesses?

**Months 1–3** — Technical foundations: indexation fixes, Core Web Vitals, structured data, Google Business Profile.

**Months 3–6** — Initial ranking improvements as topical authority content indexes. Measurable increases for mid-competition Bradford and West Yorkshire queries.

**Months 6–12** — Compound growth across topic clusters. Competitive queries in professional services, healthcare, and retail begin delivering page-one positions.

## How Much Does an SEO Consultant in Bradford Cost?

**Technical audits** — £500–£1,200 depending on site size and scope.

**Topical maps** — from £800 to £2,500+ depending on industry and topic breadth.

**Monthly retainers** — from £1,500. Independent consultant pricing typically delivers the same senior-level quality as a Leeds agency at 40–60% of the cost. Initial consultations are free.

